<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Future Simple</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/learn-grammar/present-simple.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:ital,wght@0,300..800;1,300..800&family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900&family=Sour+Gummy:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&family=Tinos:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400;1,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        .modal {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            z-index: 1;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .modal-content {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 500px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .close-btn {
            float: right;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>FUTURE SIMPLE</h1>
        <table>
            <tr class="row1">
                <td class="first-column">Affirmative</td>
                <td class="button-box" onclick="showExamples('modal1')">I <span>will</span><br>read<br>write<br>work</td>
                <td class="button-box" onclick="showExamples('modal2')">HE/SHE/IT <span>will</span><br>read<br>write<br>work</td>
                <td class="button-box" onclick="showExamples('modal3')">YOU/WE/THEY <span>will</span><br>read<br>write<br>work</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="row2">
                <td class="first-column">Question</td>
                <td class="button-box" onclick="showExamples('modal4')"><span>Will</span> I<br>read?<br>write?<br>work?</td>
                <td class="button-box" onclick="showExamples('modal5')"><span>Will</span> HE/SHE/IT<br>read?<br>write?<br>work?</td>
                <td class="button-box" onclick="showExamples('modal6')"><span>Will</span> YOU/WE/THEY<br>read?<br>write?<br>work?</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="row3">
                <td class="first-column">Negative</td>
                <td class="button-box" onclick="showExamples('modal7')">I <span>won't</span><br>read<br>write<br>work</td>
                <td class="button-box" onclick="showExamples('modal8')">HE/SHE/IT <span>won't</span><br>read<br>write<br>work</td>
                <td class="button-box" onclick="showExamples('modal9')">YOU/WE/THEY <span>won't</span><br>read<br>write<br>work</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <button class="check-knowledge-btn">Test</button>

        <div id="modal1" class="modal">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeModal('modal1')">&times;</span>
                <h2>Examples (I - Affirmative)</h2>
                <p>- I will read that book tomorrow.</p>
                <p>- I will write a letter next week.</p>
                <p>- I will work on this project later.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="modal2" class="modal">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeModal('modal2')">&times;</span>
                <h2>Examples (HE/SHE/IT - Affirmative)</h2>
                <p>- He will read the report soon.</p>
                <p>- She will write a novel someday.</p>
                <p>- It will work properly after the update.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="modal3" class="modal">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeModal('modal3')">&times;</span>
                <h2>Examples (YOU/WE/THEY - Affirmative)</h2>
                <p>- You will read this article later.</p>
                <p>- We will write a review soon.</p>
                <p>- They will work on the project tomorrow.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="modal4" class="modal">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeModal('modal4')">&times;</span>
                <h2>Examples (I - Question)</h2>
                <p>- Will I read it by the weekend?</p>
                <p>- Will I write a response soon?</p>
                <p>- Will I work on it tomorrow?</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="modal5" class="modal">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeModal('modal5')">&times;</span>
                <h2>Examples (HE/SHE/IT - Question)</h2>
                <p>- Will he read the instructions?</p>
                <p>- Will she write a poem?</p>
                <p>- Will it work without errors?</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="modal6" class="modal">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeModal('modal6')">&times;</span>
                <h2>Examples (YOU/WE/THEY - Question)</h2>
                <p>- Will you read this before the meeting?</p>
                <p>- Will we write the report together?</p>
                <p>- Will they work on the holiday?</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="modal7" class="modal">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeModal('modal7')">&times;</span>
                <h2>Examples (I - Negative)</h2>
                <p>- I won’t read that book tonight.</p>
                <p>- I won’t write the email right now.</p>
                <p>- I won’t work late today.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="modal8" class="modal">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeModal('modal8')">&times;</span>
                <h2>Examples (HE/SHE/IT - Negative)</h2>
                <p>- He won’t read the magazine.</p>
                <p>- She won’t write the article now.</p>
                <p>- It won’t work without maintenance.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="modal9" class="modal">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeModal('modal9')">&times;</span>
                <h2>Examples (YOU/WE/THEY - Negative)</h2>
                <p>- You won’t read it until later.</p>
                <p>- We won’t write the review today.</p>
                <p>- They won’t work this weekend.</p>
            </div>
        </div>


    <script>
        function showExamples(modalId) {
            document.getElementById(modalId).style.display = "flex";
        }
        function closeModal(modalId) {
            document.getElementById(modalId).style.display = "none";
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
